invalid type: string "forwarded. \n \n \n5. ROUTERS \n\u{f0a7} A router is a three-layer device.\u{f020} \n\u{f0a7} It operates in the physical, data-link, and network layers.\u{f020} \n\u{f0a7} As a physical-layer device, it regenerates the signal it receives.\u{f020} \n\u{f0a7} As a link-layer device, the router checks the physical addresses (source and destination) \ncontained in the packet.¯·╝